author: kpvdr
msg: QPID-3858: More restructuring: Renamed XXXContext to XXXAsyncContext for all async store context classes, also avoids name clash with TransactionContext, an existing non-async context class.

author: stsp
msg: (diff_repos_repos_added_or_deleted_file): Avoid direct use of the temporary
file handle by deleting the temporary file upon pool cleanup instead of when
the file is closed. This allows us to flush buffers to disk by closing the
'content' stream rather than calling flush() on the file handle.
